# {{ _service_name | title }} Service Diagram Pack

⭐ **Purpose**

Illustrate the default control flow for the generated {{ _service_name }} stack so the service owner can adapt it once custom dependencies or sidecars are added.

☑️ **Mermaid Flow**

```mermaid
flowchart LR
    Client["Client (user or upstream)"]
{% if _use_traefik %}
    Proxy["Traefik reverse proxy"]
{% endif %}
{% if _include_ui %}
    UI["{{ _service_name }}-ui (frontend)"]
{% endif %}
    Service["{{ _service_name }} (backend)"]
    Dependency["Downstream dependency"]
    Health["Health endpoint {{ _service_health_endpoint }}"]
    Observability[(Observability stack)]
{% if _enable_monitoring %}
    Metrics["Metrics collector (/metrics)"]
{% endif %}

{% if _use_traefik and _include_ui %}
    Client -->|HTTPS| Proxy
    Proxy --> UI
    UI --> Service
{% elif _use_traefik %}
    Client -->|HTTPS| Proxy
    Proxy --> Service
{% elif _include_ui %}
    Client --> UI
    UI --> Service
{% else %}
    Client --> Service
{% endif %}
    Service --> Dependency
    Service --> Health
    Service --> Observability
{% if _enable_monitoring %}
    Service -.-> Metrics
    Metrics -.-> Observability
{% endif %}
```

☑️ **Mermaid Sequence**

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client
{% if _use_traefik %}
    participant Proxy as Traefik
{% endif %}
{% if _include_ui %}
    participant UI as {{ _service_name }}-ui
{% endif %}
    participant Service as {{ _service_name }}
    participant Dependency as Downstream dependency
    participant Observability as Observability pipeline
{% if _enable_monitoring %}
    participant Metrics as Metrics collector
{% endif %}

{% if _use_traefik and _include_ui %}
    Client->>Proxy: HTTPS request for UI
    Proxy->>UI: Forward request
    UI-->>Client: Rendered view
    UI->>Proxy: API call (/api/...)
    Proxy->>Service: Forward API call
{% elif _use_traefik %}
    Client->>Proxy: HTTPS request
    Proxy->>Service: Routed request
{% elif _include_ui %}
    Client->>UI: HTTP request
    UI->>Service: API call
{% else %}
    Client->>Service: Request
{% endif %}
    Service->>Dependency: Query/command
    Dependency-->>Service: Result
    Service-->>Client: Response
    Service--)Observability: Log/trace event
{% if _enable_monitoring %}
    Metrics->>Service: Scrape /metrics
    Service-->>Metrics: Metrics data
{% endif %}
```

✅ **Implementation Notes**

- Replace the `Downstream dependency` placeholder with real integrations such as databases, queues, or external APIs.
- Extend the diagrams when adding sidecars (migrations, workers, cron jobs) so the operational runbooks stay accurate.
- Ensure docker-compose overrides or k8s manifests remain in sync with this documentation when topologies change.
- Export finalized diagrams as SVG/PNG (`mmdc`) to embed in higher-level design docs or dashboards.
